### Получение товара,списка товаров
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/product/
Content-Type: application/json

### Создание товара
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/product/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token 7b27e08f875629bc60a1a1c678a3d9d59ab60854

{
    "title":"Lenovo 222",
    "description":"best",
    "price": 1500
}

### Изменение товара
PATCH  http://localhost:8000/api/v1/product/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token 7b27e08f875629bc60a1a1c678a3d9d59ab60854

{
    "title":"Lenovo 222",
    "description":"best",
    "price": 1500
}

### Удаление товаров
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/product/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token 7b27e08f875629bc60a1a1c678a3d9d59ab60854

